Heritage-Crystal Clean, Inc Key Developments

Heritage-Crystal Clean Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Second Quarter and Six Months Ended June 20, 2017
Jul 25 17
Heritage-Crystal Clean Inc. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the second quarter and six months ended June 20, 2017. For the quarter, the company reported revenues of $86.382 million compared to $80.552 million a year ago. Operating income was $11.380 million against $3.344 million last year. Income before income taxes was $10.968 million against $2.893 million last year. Net income attributable to company common stockholders was $6.934 million or $0.30 per basic and diluted share against $1.831 million or $0.08 per basic and diluted share last year. EBITDA was $15.564 million against $7.462 million last year. Adjusted EBITDA was $12.643 million against $9.852 million last year. Adjusted net earnings were $4,558,000 or $0.19 per diluted share compared to $2,812,000 or $0.13 per diluted share a year ago.


For the six months, the company reported revenues of $166.835 million, compared to $159.005 million a year ago. Operating income was $19.076 million against $1.272 million last year. Income before income taxes was $18.577 million against $0.303 million last year. Net income attributable to company common stockholders was $11.698 or $0.51 per basic and diluted share against $0.064 million or $0.00 per basic and diluted share last year. EBITDA was $27.392 million against $9.518 million last year. Adjusted EBITDA was $20.729 million against $15.167 million last year.


Heritage-Crystal Clean, Inc to Report Q2, 2017 Results on Jul 25, 2017
Jul 11 17
Heritage-Crystal Clean, Inc announced that they will report Q2, 2017 results at 5:00 PM, Eastern Standard Time on Jul 25, 2017


